Class ClassNotFoundException

java.lang.Object
  org.jscripter.emu.java.lang.Throwable
      org.jscripter.emu.java.lang.Exception
          org.jscripter.emu.java.lang.ClassNotFoundException

public class ClassNotFoundException
extends Exception

An internal class of an exception thrown when an application tries to load in a class but no definition for the class with the specified name could be found, emulating a standard java.lang interface or class with the same simple name as this one.

This interface or class is only used internally by JS re-compiler implementations.

Please refer to the Java API Standards for detail description of the original class or interface.

Author:
J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.jscripter.org
JavaScript:
Re-compilers must redirect the resolution of the emulated original Java class or interface to this one.
